            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[## MacHelper Pro 1.0.0 (4)

- Shows the update-check dialog before Sparkle starts its installer-status probe, so feedback appears immediately even when that probe takes several seconds.
- Adds more update-check timing diagnostics around the preflight window, Sparkle handoff, and result callbacks.
]]></description>
